          """savvy; A person from an arid region is not likely to know how to live in more "civilized" society"""'\n'
          "and often acclimates slowly in any region other than one that's heated.")
if placeanswer == "info seas":
    print("Whether it be on a massive floating city or bustling port, people close to the sea are resilient are as"'\n'
          "they come. Typically in tight-knit communities a person will know how to communicate well and if"'\n'
          "you're looking to travel the high seas there's no better way than to have a savvy sailor by your side."'\n'
